title: Sunny and Spacious 2 Bedroom brand new apt with vineyard views!
posting_body: ['Welcome to The NOTL Village Apartments.', 'This newly built walk-up apartment with a vineyard view on both floors, tons of windows, and a wonderful landlord, is located within the historic Old Town Niagara-on-The-Lake.', 'This apt over two floors has all brand new appliances, hardwood floors, high ceilings, and multiple vineyard views from its many windows.', 'It has two massive bathrooms with tubs, another bathroom on the main floor.', 'It is also quiet, and has really nice neighbours, and pets are welcome!!', 'The Village is an award-winning master planned community.', 'Within the neighbourhood, you will find wonderfully walkable streets, a beautiful diversity of architecture, an array of small parks, and a mix of residential houses with commercial restaurants, stores, and gorgeous paths through the woods to a creek which then leads into the town of Niagara on the Lake.', 'Includes a parking space and visitor parking and a bike storage shed.', 'For more details on the property and a video walk through - <URL>']
